GoBoost is a business web-based software designed to connect service contractors with their customers virtually. This Chrome Extension extends the power of the GoBoost platform and allows customers to use GoBoost's features across the web.

Note: an active subscription to GoBoost is required to use this extension. Please visit goboost.com for more information.
